cat << EOF
Free Philips USB Webcam driver for Linux that supports VGA resolution, newer kernels and replacing the old pwcx module. 

This is a fork of the discontinuity pwc driver made by Nemosoft Unv. You don't need binary module with this driver, however decompression is supported for big resolution (640x480). The driver is designed for Linux 2.6, patches for 2.4 is not tested.
EOF
